<P>
   COXNET PTECH 0718 _ Are you scared of Web surfing? Terrified of
technology? You are not alone. And there is help. Getting plugged
in to the information revolution is easier than you think. You may
even find that it's fun (Katz, Atlanta Journal-Constitution.) Art
includes a 4-column color photo of Microsoft's ``Digital Diva''
