<HEADLINE>
THEME PLAYERS  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  ATTENTION EDITORS: The following material from The New York Times
Syndicate is for use by clients of ``HIGH STYLE AND MORE.''
Nonsubscribers can use this article only by special arrangement.
For purchase information, see end of text. 
 &HT;    
 (Four color slides are available.) 
 From WWD 
 (Distributed by New York Times Special Features) 
 &HT;    NEW YORK _ Resort means different things to different designers,
but this season there's a common thread _ a feminine touch.
 &HT;    At Oscar de la Renta, for example, colorful silk chiffon pieces
with pretty beading are perfect for the party set, while at Narciso
Rodriguez, city looks are more important than tropical locales.
 &HT;    Accordingly, he's offering lots of sleek suede and leather in
soft neutrals and blush tones.
 c.2000 Fairchild Publications 
