<HEADLINE>
MASTER BLEND  
 &HT;   
</HEADLINE>
  ATTENTION EDITORS: The following material from The New York Times
Syndicate is for use by clients of ``HIGH STYLE AND MORE.''
Nonsubscribers can use this article only by special arrangement.
For purchase information, see end of text. 
 &HT;    
 (Three color slides are available.) 
 From WWD 
 (Distributed by New York Times Special Features) 
 &HT;    The lure of the ladylike is at a fever pitch. And for resort,
there are lots of different interpretations of the trend.
 &HT;    Ann Sui, who's usually in retro bohemian mode, has combined both
elements, while Richard Tyler keeps things extra sexy.
 &HT;    Gianfranco Ferre, on the other hand, gives it to us straight in
the form of clean classics.
 c.2000 Fairchild Publications 
