 &HT;    c.2000 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   ICANN AT A GLANCE
</P>
<P>
   Name: Internet Corporation for Assigned Names and Numbers.
</P>
<P>
   Founded: First met in November 1998
</P>
<P>
   What it is: A non-profit organization based in California.
</P>
<P>
   Purpose: To take over administration of the Internet address
system from the U.S. government.
</P>
<P>
   Responsibilities: Manage the Internet's root servers; settle
