   &UR; SPORTS (s) &LR;
</P>
<P>
   GLF-BRITISH-VANDEVELDE (Undated) _ Jean Van de Velde returns to
the british Open, having not lost his grip after last year's major
disappointment. By Jim McCabe. (2 takes)
</P>
<P>
   &UR; The Boston Globe &LR;  &QC;
</P>
