   IMMIGRANT-VOTERS _ WASHINGTON _ Millions of recently naturalized
immigrants are eligible to vote for president for the first time in
the November elections, and some analysts predict they could be a
deciding factor in key electoral states. (Garcia, Cox News
Service).
