<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 2000-07-17 21:31 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4990 &Cx1f; tta-z
u a BC-NY-HAMPTONS-WEALTH-AR     07-17 0967
